short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get IDs on Facebook, Instagram, and Tiktok.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "SocialID Tracker" is a Chrome extension that quickly and easily retrieves Facebook, Instagram, and TikTok IDs, making it a useful tool for social media research, analysis, and marketing purposes. With its simple and intuitive interface, users can efficiently obtain unique user identifiers and improve their social media strategies.
